FireRedASR2 supports Chinese (Mandarin, 20+ dialects/accents), English, code-switching, and singing lyrics recognition. FireRedVAD supports speech/singing/music in 100+ langs. FireRedLID supports 100+ langs and 20+ zh dialects.
